## Phase 3 тАФ Run the Demo (Ready)

Follow the official `DEMODEPLOYMENT.md` instructions:
1. Ensure `.env` is properly populated.
2. Run `docker-compose build --no-cache`.
3. Run `docker-compose up -d --force-recreate`.
4. Apply migrations: `docker-compose exec backend python manage.py migrate`.
5. Create admin: `docker-compose exec backend python manage.py createsuperuser`.
6. Import eBooks: `docker-compose exec backend python manage.py imports_assets`.
7. Download the AI Model: `docker-compose exec ollama ollama run qwen2.5:1.5b`.
8. Access http://localhost:3000 (webpage) and http://localhost:3001/admin (admin) to verify.

